Description: <h1 align="center">Python_Brokers_API</h1>
        <p align="center">This repository hosts the brain api used for my trading algorithms.</p> 
        
        <div align="center">
          <strong>Simple functions to use crypto brokers with python 3 </strong>
        </div>
        
        <br />
        
